            <title>[SOLR-5479] SolrCmdDistributor retry logic stops if a leader for the request cannot be found in 1 second.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5479</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This causes the request to fail - which is fine - but ideally it would keep retrying until it found the new leader - at least for a few more seconds than 1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
